          "order": 3,
          "title": "CONTRACTS YOU SHOULD NEVER SIGN",
          "summary": "When it comes to software engineering and the IT industry in general, contracts are a necessary part of doing business. In this article, the author shares his experience with various contracts and legal documents. He lists out types of contracts he recommends a developer should not sign, such as an employee contract that contains any form of a non-compete clause.",
